WRITING.TEXT: My redo of TruePower Betty #8203; Changes: #8203; TruePower Betty gains new 2 bars : Magic and HATE #8203; Magic drains slowly as Betty begins to slowly hyper-heal at 80 percent stamina and more (similar to Undyne's ability to use DETERMINATION to heal herself). #8203; As Magic reaches Zero, it can't be generated again and Betty relies on HATE. HATE's effects remain mostly similar, though it only lowers her DEF (her ATK is still 65, if it drops to 0, then you're fucked, even if you have like, 250 DEF left from HATE.) #8203; MOVESET CHANGES: TruePower Betty #8203; (F - "Shields made of FEAR"): Betty forms her arms into 2 shields made of the same material as Akumu, crouching and putting them infront of her, hiding her body and face, ready to block incoming attacks. Any attacks that are blocked do not do any damage or will have the damage reduced significantly. If too many attacks are blocked, Betty will be stunned, leaving her open for attacks. There are some exceptions to what can and can't be blocked. #8203; ( Right Click - "Beatdown of a Beast" ): Strong Combo consisting 1 special move (used 3 times) and 2 other moves. Betty latching onto the foe with Akumu formed into a line (similar to Basophobia) and slamming them into the ground 3 times, before dashing towards them and stabbing through the stomach, bashing them 2 times again after with her claws, and then punching them fullforce away, dealing great knockback. The first three attacks respectively deal 86 DMG each, while the 4th attack deals 101, the 5th and 6th attacks dealing both 116 DMG each, and the last punch dealing 159 DMG. ( DONE ON A DEF 1 ATTACK DUMMY. ) #8203; (6 - "Ballistophobia V2") (CD 55s): Betty crouches and crosses her arms, as 4 beams of dark-pink magical energy burst from her back, homing towards the target, similar to GTC's DT 4. Each beam deals a respective 56 DMG plus big knockback (like, CG Sword Knockback.) Deals a total of 224 DMG. ( DONE ON A DEF 1 ATTACK DUMMY. ) #8203; (7 - "Chirophobia") (CD 20s): Betty clenches her fist, as Akumu gives her more magical energy to her clenched fist, making it grow in size, charging it up with a 0.5 second delay before it punches the person full force, knocking them back. Takes a small bit of mana and deals 254 DMG. ( DONE ON A DEF 1 ATTACK DUMMY. ) #8203; (8 - "Sheltoelnophobia") (CD 50s): Betty rushes the victim and punches them in the gut, before immediately crouching and grabbing them with her hand, which is now 25x bigger, similar to Aviatophobia's attack. She begins to crush the foe, draining their HP before she flings them away. Takes a small bit of mana and deals 142 Primary DMG and 56 Drain DMG. ( DONE ON A DEF 1 ATTACK DUMMY. ) #8203; (9 - "Belonephobia: Ultimate") (CD 1m30s): Betty slams both her hands into the floor, vocalizing a slight noise reminiscent of that of a rattlesnake, before multiple spikes surround the victim and, with a 0.5 second delay, stab into them, slamming them down. After they get up, they'll be stunned for around 3 seconds, similar to Cross and XChara's ERASE\_CODE. Takes a mediocre amount of mana and deals 457 DMG. ( DONE OF A DEF 1 ATTACK DUMMY. ) #8203; (UNLOCKABLE IF YOU HAVE 2 SOULs OR MORE IN BASE OR HATE MODE) #8203; (10 - "True Rhabdophobia" ) #8203; Betty will cry out, "Rhabdophobia!" and release a barrier around her. Inside, colors are inverted. Projectiles/mana based attacks that touch the barrier will turn white and freeze, then quickly turn around and fly back to the opponent who launched them. This includes, but is not limited to, Gaster Blasters, knife projectiles, Chara's slashes, and Hate Bomb. Takes up a large amount of mana. #8203;
